OL,3,CLiveable neighbourhood scheme delayed
OL,4,Cyet again
OL,6,FPlans for a liveable neighbourhood
OL,7,Fscheme in east Bristol have been
OL,8,Fdelayed until the end of the year.
OL,10,FBristol City Council has said that the
OL,11,FEast Bristol Liveable Neighbourhood
OL,12,Ftrial will now be installed in
OL,13,FNovember and December.
OL,15,FThe scheme has been planned for
OL,16,Fseveral years, but its rollout has
OL,17,Fbeen repeatedly pushed back. It
OL,18,Finvolves new bus gates, bollards and
OL,19,Fone-way systems to prevent drivers
OL,20,Ffrom taking shortcuts through
OL,21,Fresidential streets.
