OL,3,CLiveable neighbourhood scheme delayed
OL,4,Cyet again
OL,6,F"We're confident these upcoming
OL,7,Fchanges will make the liveable
OL,8,Fneighbourhood a safer and healthier
OL,9,Fplace to live with quiet streets that
OL,10,Fare less congested and polluted. It's
OL,11,Fimportant to emphasise that all areas
OL,12,Fof the neighbourhood will still be
OL,13,Faccessible by motorised vehicles, but
OL,14,Froutes may change."
OL,16,FIn spring 2023, the council said the
OL,17,Fproject was due to start in the autumn
OL,18,Flater that year. It was then pushed
OL,19,Fback to last winter, then this summer
OL,20,Fand now the latest scheduled roll-out
OL,21,Fis November and December this year.
